creator: Shenzhen Proscenic Technology Co.,Ltd
descriptionHtml:
"The Vactidy App is a mobile phone application that connects Vactidy smart products. You can control the functions of the product and monitor your product in real-time through the application. Here, you can control the product anytime and anywhere, and you can also streamline communication between smart devices. Intercommunication makes the product more portable and smart during use.


Linkage control, easy to use
We want you to experience a smarter and more portable lifestyle. The app is simple to operate and you can quickly add a variety of home appliances while performing linkage operations to interconnect smart devices.

Share your joy with just one-click
We want to add more fun to your life. With simple one-click sharing, you can share your device with family and friends, manage it remotely, experience convenience, and enjoy the fun of science and technology together.

Connect to the Internet in no time
After connecting to your smart device, you can
(1) Start and pause your robot remotely
(2) View the cleaning map and understand the robot cleaning area
(3) Set the cleaning mode you want to track cleaning tasks

Download now and experience this house cleaning ""beast"" by Vactidy."

descriptionHtml:
Explore the Vactidy App and Light Up Your Smart Life!
This amazing mobile application connects you with your smart devices, giving you effortless control over everything. Like magic, you can monitor and operate your devices in real time. No matter where you are, enjoy convenient control anytime, anywhere, and simplify interactions between smart devices.

Integrated Control for Greater Convenience!
We aim to provide you with a integrated and flexible lifestyle. With an intuitive and easy-to-use interface, you can effortlessly add appliances and enable seamless connections between smart devices, delivering unmatched convenience.

Share Joy with One Tap—Endless Fun!
Our goal is to bring more joy to your life. With a single tap, share devices with family and friends, manage them remotely, and fully embrace the fun of technology.

Connect to the Internet and Enjoy Unparalleled Convenience!
Once connected to smart devices, you can easily:
1. Start and pause your robot remotely.
2. View the cleaning map to see the robot's cleaning progress.
3. Set cleaning modes and track cleaning tasks.

Download now to experience the Vactidy cleaning "beast" and give your home a sparkling transformation!
